name: SPECIAL EDITION: BLACKHOLEBOY
description:
BLACKHOLE is a boy from a legendary alien civilization. His sight has one of the most terrifying effects in our universe, it is impossible for anyone to escape it. He can compress all the mass in an infinitesimal point of his brain creating a gravitational field so extreme that he is able to bend space-time and attract anyone who approaches him.
He is a very dangerous boy for both his teammates and his enemies.
All the other alien races respect him and, naturally, he has become the commander of the GALACTICBOY$ division of our gang.
